ingredient: Salt and Freshly Cracked Pepper to taste
6 oz. chopped kale (1/2 of a 12oz. bag)
1 cup room temperature salted butter (plus more for greasing)
1.5 cups all-purpose flour (plus more for dusting)
1/4 tsp freshly cracked black pepper (or to taste)
1 pinch crushed red pepper (or to taste)
1 Tbsp vegetable shortening, oil, or butter
